<h1 class="hero-h">2026 fitness AI tool <em style="color:#00C853;font-style:italic;">reference.</em></h1>
<p class="hero-sub">A 2026 reference covering the AI tools fitness operators actually evaluate — purpose-built AI agent platforms, gym CRM AI features, horizontal AI tools, and how they fit together. Built for multi-unit operators, franchisees, and independent gyms making buying decisions. Citable; refreshed quarterly.</p>
